  "instructions": [
    "Place the molcajete and grind the onion, ginger, and garlic until smooth.",
    "Transfer the ground mixture to a bowl and add lime juice, soy sauce, vinegar, paprika, chili powder, cilantro, and salt, then stir to combine.",
    "In a separate bowl, gently shred the 200g bonito fillet into thin strips and lay them over the citrus mixture, then let marinate for 5 minutes.",
    "Meanwhile, scoop 50g of cooked vialone nano rice into individual serving bowls.",
    "Spoon the marinated bonito mixture over the rice, ensuring an even layer.",
    "Chill the ceviche in the refrigerator for 10 minutes before serving."
